      "content": "it just feels like there's no light at the end of this. like, what's the point of trying to \"endure\" it when the end result is just more emptiness? i look at the future and i see nothing. just more mornings of this exact same pain. it feels like the only way to actually get peace is to just... stop. to stop feeling. to just be done with it.",
